Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A prime opportunity exists to secure a fully fitted and furnished office on Level 3 of the South Shore Centre.

The tenancy boasts excellent views of the river and city.

The tenancy has a modern fitout including a reception area, board room, meeting room, 5 offices, 30 work stations, store room, utitiy area, comms room, kitchen and breakout area.

The occupies a prestigious location on the South Perth Esplanade providing easy access to the freeway system and direct access to the CBD by ferry from across the road. An array of amenity is on the doorstep including restaurants, cafes, supermarket, banks, post office and the Windsor Hotel.

The building also has a public car park (free for the 1st hour) and End of Trip facilities.

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact Luke Bray 0403 184 340, luke.bray@cbre.com.au

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FULLY FITTED OFFICE - RIVER & CITY VIEWS

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Excellent views of CBD and Swan River
High car bay allocation, with no levy

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The South Shore Centre is a high-quality office development in a prestigious location on the corner of the South Perth Esplanade and Mends Street, right on the Swan River.

The building has restaurants and retail offerings on the ground level and is close to banks, cafes, the post office and the Windsor Hotel.

Areas available: 

Level 3 - 356sqm: partitioned with reception area, board room, 2 meeting rooms, 3 offices, open plan work stations, kitchen and store room. 

Level 4 - 240sqm: partitioned with reception area, board room, meeting room, 6 offices, store / utility area and kitchen.

Level 3 - 481sqm: partitioned tenancy with a reception area, board room, meeting room, 5 offices, 30 work stations, store room print room, comms room, kitchen and breakout area. 

Building features include:

- Excellent views of the Swan River and CBD.
- An abundant of client/visitor parking (first hour free).
- Easy access to the freeway North and South.
- Direct ferry access to Elizabeth Quay from Mends Street Jetty
- Secure under cover car parking available (1 bay per 30sqm)
- End of Trip facilities (bike racks, lockers & showers)

Located in the middle of Perth’s most iconic and picturesque streets, Unit 8 / 25- 35 Mends Street, South Perth is surrounded by prominent food & beverage operators, fashion retailers and local amenities, benefiting from the expansion in residential development and population growth.   

Offering 88sqm* of multi-use capability, this first floor re-furbished tenancy has freshly painted walls, split-cycle air-conditioning, suspended ceilings, storage options and CCTV security. 

The unique tenancy is the perfect entry level Office, Retail or QSR opportunity for a new/established business to join the transformation of South Perth. 
 
Additional features include:

+ 2 Car-parking bays 
+ Mends street exposure
+ Fascia signage 
+ Multiple uses (Subject to Council Approval)
+ Popular retail/shopping precinct
+ 100m to Windsor Hotel
+ 200m to South Perth foreshore 
+ 300m to Perth Zoo
+ Surrounded by prominent local amenity

Zoning:

This property is zoned ‘Mends Street Centre Commercial’ under the City of South Perth’s Local Town Planning Scheme No.6. 

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the Leasing Agent.

* Approx
* Subject to Council Approval
